icon is really specific for the, like, the way that

00:12:53.380 --> 00:12:55.110
Atproto is set up, but we wanted to have

00:12:55.110 --> 00:12:56.100
our own schema system.

00:12:56.110 --> 00:12:58.780
So we have, like, a lightweight way of, like

00:12:58.780 --> 00:13:00.520
, doing this across platform.

