Right now it's sort of is, like, using JSON

00:13:02.410 --> 00:13:05.100
schema as an intermediary, but we want to support other

00:13:05.280 --> 00:13:06.380
things for that also.

00:13:06.390 --> 00:13:08.510
But essentially, like, when you have a data set that

00:13:08.580 --> 00:13:10.500
you're loading out from the world, you want to be

